    <p>{`No; existing open incidents will remain in their current state.`}</p>
    <p>{`Moreover, incidents will not be automatically resolved through the Events API either. Maintenance mode is like flipping the "off" switch for all integrations; no actions can be taken through the Events API for all of that service's integrations when it is in a maintenance period, or disabled.`}</p>

